  <h1>Universal Map Generator (UMG)</h1>

  <div class="section">
    <p><strong>UMG</strong> is a scripting language for generating random maps of any kind. It's designed to be lightweight and easy to integrate into your game. KeeperRL supports it as part of its modding and procedural generation systems.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Why Use UMG?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Quickly test and iterate on your layouts using the standalone tool.</li>
      <li>Extend your gameâ€™s functionality with modding-friendly map generation scripts.</li>
      <li>Create rich, random environments for dungeons, overworlds, or abstract layouts.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

