  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Tip for Modders</h2>
    <p>You can write random map generation scripts in <code>umg</code> format and plug them into your KeeperRL mods. This opens up advanced procedural content design for faction bases, surface encounters, custom dungeon branches, and more.</p>
